Bee Noir is alJazari[1] in python plus hexagons in 2D

the webserver code is based on polosc[2]

dependencies:
 - python
 - pyglet
 - pyOSC
 - SuperCollider

to start:
 1) start the webserver:
	cd web/
	python polosc/polosc.py 8000 cs.map cs.not
 2) start SuperCollider or something else listening on port 57120
 3) start the game:
	python aljasari.py


You can receive actions with OSC in e. g. SuperCollider:
	port: 57120
	address: /alj/action 
	format: player_id (int), 
		x-position (float), 
		y-position (float), 
		tile-value (float),
		quantisation (int)

To control a player go to http://127.0.0.1:8000/


[1] http://pawfal.org/index.php?page=AlJazari
[2] http://www.pillowsopher.com/blog/?p=107